Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.30,0:01:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fad(777,853)\fnBook Antiqua\fs32\b1\bord0\shad1\4c&HB7B7BA&\pos(320,430)\c&H3435B9&}~Maiden of Despair: Ren Yuuki~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.27,0:01:41.89,MD2RY - ITA,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what it was about that girl that drew me to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.72,0:01:46.48,MD2RY - ITA,,0000,0000,0000,,If I had to guess,\N I'd say it was her innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.98,0:01:51.03,MD2RY - ITA,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like a magnetic pole\N will attract its opposite,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.00,0:01:54.82,MD2RY - ITA,,0000,0000,0000,,she attracted the dark \Nand sordid side of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.81,0:02:08.80,MD2RY - ITA,,0000,0000,0000,,But what was she waiting for during those many months?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.31,0:02:13.80,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.80,0:02:15.97,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold your horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.08,0:03:45.10,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,This looks bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.10,0:03:47.53,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,But I might be able\N to do something about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.53,0:03:49.38,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll begin treatment right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.38,0:03:50.70,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.04,0:03:56.48,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Is your house nearby?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.34,0:03:57.91,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.03,0:04:00.20,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,The weather's getting worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.27,0:04:26.32,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.84,0:04:29.69,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all out of money,\N so this is all I can give you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.41,0:04:35.65,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine. You go ahead and eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.65,0:04:38.22,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, I'm not hungry at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.31,0:04:43.93,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think your stomach's rumbling in agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.94,0:04:46.62,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.62,0:04:47.02,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.02,0:04:50.08,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case,\N I {\i1}will{\i0} go ahead and eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.09,0:04:54.80,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, who's "Fahm"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.13,0:04:59.61,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,You were saying that name over and over in your sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.61,0:05:01.27,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,That's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.36,0:05:05.09,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.73,0:05:08.59,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,It's going to get colder.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.59,0:05:12.23,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you going to do?\N You won't survive here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.23,0:05:15.97,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,My father will come for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.43,0:05:19.26,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I don't have \Nanywhere else to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.63,0:05:23.67,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't mind,\N you can come along with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.92,0:05:32.39,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she's an Oriental.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.39,0:05:34.63,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,And a young one, at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.63,0:05:38.22,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, let her stay here\N for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.22,0:05:39.67,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put her to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.67,0:05:40.72,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll be useful to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.08,0:05:42.03,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Her name?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.46,0:05:44.97,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Ren Yuuki, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.55,0:05:49.47,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you a trial period.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.47,0:05:54.61,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,During your stay at my home, you must follow all the rules of the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.25,0:05:56.69,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.69,0:05:57.70,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.16,0:06:02.26,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.27,0:06:08.43,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Ren, this will be \Nyour room from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.50,0:06:26.16,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did Foster go?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.05,0:06:29.16,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently he had\N some investigating to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.16,0:06:31.34,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,He's leaving Ren\N in our care for 2-3 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.20,0:07:09.01,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,I sincerely apologize for my lateness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.01,0:07:13.25,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm. So was your investigation fruitful?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.80,0:07:16.42,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I believe you will be satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.42,0:07:17.78,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.64,0:07:20.90,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.29,0:07:23.71,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.13,0:07:28.09,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.59,0:07:30.62,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be counting on you in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.35,0:07:31.87,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.35,0:07:33.80,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.89,0:07:45.28,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,You called for me, Mr. Dred?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.28,0:07:47.47,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.71,0:07:53.65,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you're a good worker, Ren.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.65,0:07:55.39,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.96,0:07:57.85,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,I have good news for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.85,0:08:01.12,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,We've received word from your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.12,0:08:03.41,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? From my father?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.41,0:08:05.53,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,He should be here for you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.94,0:08:10.12,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, hurry back to your\N room and wait for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.50,0:08:11.45,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.44,0:08:19.39,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Father...\NI get to see him...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.39,0:08:21.74,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Father... father!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.14,0:08:29.53,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew my father would\N come and find me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.10,0:08:35.37,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Ren, is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.37,0:08:36.70,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Fa...ther?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:40.18,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Ren, I missed you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.18,0:08:41.07,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Ren!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.37,0:08:42.68,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.04,0:08:45.16,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me get a good look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.16,0:08:46.84,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are Ren, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.58,0:08:50.59,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooohhh, my sweet little Ren!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.59,0:08:53.02,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Ren, Ren!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.02,0:08:55.61,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that tickles, Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.50,0:09:05.79,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.65,0:09:11.78,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.90,0:09:12.79,MD2RY - OVR,,0000,0000,0000,,No, stop it, Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.01,0:09:15.71,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,No... no...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.29,0:09:19.96,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,No... stop it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.81,0:09:22.35,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,How about {\i1}this{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.09,0:09:21.95,MD2RY - OVR,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.63,0:09:30.87,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,P-please stop, Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.00,0:09:37.49,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.24,0:09:47.07,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't do this, Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:49.13,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.04,0:10:01.90,MD2RY - ITA,,0000,0000,0000,,No...he isn't my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.90,0:10:03.95,MD2RY - ITA,,0000,0000,0000,,He'd never do something so awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.77,0:10:11.75,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.16,0:10:26.38,MD2RY - ITA,,0000,0000,0000,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.94,0:10:29.39,MD2RY - ITA,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to my real father...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.83,0:10:42.97,MD2RY - ITA,,0000,0000,0000,,Father! Father?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.42,0:10:46.37,MD2RY - ITA,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}FATHER!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.47,0:10:49.92,MD2RY - ITA,,0000,0000,0000,,My father...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.67,0:10:52.24,MD2RY - ITA,,0000,0000,0000,,... is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.90,0:11:20.00,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that? Did you\N know about this, Clair?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.00,0:11:21.91,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I didn't... wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.70,0:11:25.41,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait! Just leave\N the matter alone for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.41,0:11:26.54,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.37,0:11:30.96,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,What might this be?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.96,0:11:33.03,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like an old newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.54,0:11:37.68,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,"While en route to the station,"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.68,0:11:39.22,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,"a man and a woman were\N victims of a robbery."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.22,0:11:40.58,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,"The man: deceased."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.58,0:11:42.87,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,"The surviving woman:\N lost consciousness."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.87,0:11:45.20,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hair: Black.\N Eyes: Green."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.20,0:11:47.05,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,This is talking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.70,0:11:49.44,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Ren?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.29,0:12:02.32,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.32,0:12:05.53,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I told you\N never to question me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.06,0:12:07.16,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.54,0:12:08.56,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,No more!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.56,0:12:10.83,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl is a resident\N of this mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.83,0:12:14.11,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,In accordance with the rules,\N she must entertain its guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.58,0:12:16.85,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you there when\N she agreed to that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.85,0:12:19.48,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,...on the day she came here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.44,0:12:27.76,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Bear in mind that you too\N have duties to fulfill, Foster.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.97,0:12:39.09,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm to blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.92,0:12:42.95,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,If only I'd been\N a little more careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.23,0:12:47.09,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wash away...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.09,0:12:49.51,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,...all the bad things \Nthat have happened to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.43,0:14:19.63,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm against this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.50,0:14:22.80,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,She's too young.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.04,0:14:27.55,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,I can do it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.06,0:14:29.44,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so conceited.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.92,0:14:33.47,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as Dred said before,\N there are all kinds of guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.06,0:14:35.84,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,If there are guests\N who prefer you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.41,0:14:38.31,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,...there are also ones who prefer Ren.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.89,0:15:01.79,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't forgotten the promise I made with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.79,0:15:04.02,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Go back to bed,\N in your own room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.61,0:16:54.31,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Ren, you mustn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.92,0:16:56.36,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Spread your legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.42,0:18:10.66,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,You've become so\N obedient in so little time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.19,0:18:13.96,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.96,0:18:17.11,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive, Foster.\N Most impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.03,0:18:37.85,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,What a cute little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.74,0:18:42.07,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.07,0:18:43.76,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Does she suit your tastes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.76,0:18:46.98,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. "Playtime" with her\N should be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.68,0:18:50.63,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, enjoy yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.02,0:18:53.24,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of things, Mr. Foster.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.67,0:18:54.70,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.52,0:18:58.76,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, come on over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.76,0:18:59.91,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.99,0:19:25.04,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.60,0:19:48.60,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.26,0:20:02.40,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,No...no...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.40,0:20:04.40,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,No...stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.40,0:20:05.97,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.03,0:20:11.76,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.69,0:20:16.13,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.13,0:20:17.15,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.31,0:20:22.29,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,You showed me yours,\N so I'll show you mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.11,0:20:24.83,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.28,0:21:37.41,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,No...noooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.98,0:21:41.72,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.72,0:21:44.97,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.99,0:21:50.65,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,NOOOO!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.65,0:21:52.65,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.76,0:22:35.23,MD2RY - ITA,,0000,0000,0000,,Father! Father!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.54,0:22:49.71,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Ren!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.67,0:22:57.71,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember teaching you {\i1}that{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.73,0:23:02.74,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Ren!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.46,0:23:04.59,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,That's an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.08,0:23:15.90,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,That's about enough.\N Put it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.74,0:23:20.56,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I want to be\N with my father...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.23,0:23:25.52,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.19,0:23:32.75,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.67,0:23:34.99,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,You're {\i1}not{\i0} alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.84,0:25:53.79,MD2RY - ITA,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.55,0:25:58.57,MD2RY - ITA,,0000,0000,0000,,You can make new memories that will put your mind at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.43,0:26:11.97,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Mr. Foster.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.05,0:26:16.94,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to your hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.94,0:26:19.53,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Ren asked me to cut it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.84,0:26:26.59,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me stay here for awhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.47,0:26:31.02,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to? Well, you'd better work your hardest.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.02,0:26:32.25,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.93,0:26:35.99,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's you!\N You're all better now!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.99,0:26:37.14,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.14,0:26:39.14,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,How cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.00,0:26:43.83,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,Clair, do you know who "Fahm" is?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.91,0:27:03.76,MD2RY,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the one who created this garden.
